:00（※土・日・祝は除く）</div>\n        </div><!--menu-tel-area-->\n       </div><!--right-->\n      </div><!--menuContact-area-->\n     </div><!--menu--insert-->\n    </div><!--menu-->\n  </div>\n </div><!--globalmenu-->\n</div><!--header--insert-->\n</header>\n\n<header class=\"header__container--sp\">\n <div class=\"header__insert--sp\">\n\t\t<div class=\"header__logo--sp\"><a href=\"/\"><img src=\"/asset/img/logo-sp.png\"/></a></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"menuRight\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"hamburger\">\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"menu-trigger\" href=\"javascript:;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t</div><!--hamburger-->\n\t\t</div><!--menuRight-->\n\t</div><!--wrap-->\n\t\n\t<nav class=\"slide__menu\">\n    <div class=\"slide__global\">\n      <div class=\"slide__logo\"><a href=\"/\"><img src=\"/asset/img/logo.png\"/></a></div>\n      <div class=\"menu__list--sp\">\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"/reason/\">選ばれる理由</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/quality/\">私たちのこだわり</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/promise/\">お客様との約束</a></li>\n          <li class=\"sp-acd\">\n           <dl>\n            <dt><a href=\"#\" class=\"noevent\">事業内容</a></dt>\n            <dd>\n             <p><a href=\"/business/\"><span>事業内容TOP</span></a></p>\n             <p><a href=\"/business/logistics-packaging/\"><span>物流包装事業</span></a></p>\n             <p><a href=\"/business/iron-and-steel/\"><span>鉄鋼事業</span></a></p>\n             <p><a href=\"/business/oversea/\"><span>海外事業</span></a></p>\n            </dd>\n           </dl>\n          </li>\n          <li><a href=\"/product/\">商品紹介</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/case/\">導入実績</a></li>\n          <li class=\"sp-acd\">\n           <dl>\n            <dt><a href=\"#\" class=\"noevent\">私たちについて</a></dt>\n            <dd>\n             <p><a href=\"/about/keyword/\"><span>キーワードで知る</span></a></p>\n             <p><a href=\"/about/message/\"><span>代表メッセージ・企業理念</span></a></p>\n             <p><a href=\"/about/outline/\"><span>会社概要・ネットワーク</span></a></p>\n             <p><a href=\"/about/project/\"><span>私たちの取り組み</span></a></p>\n            </dd>\n           </dl>\n          </li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://shinwa-co.co.jp/recruit/\" target=\"_blank\">採用情報</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div><!--menulist-->\n      <div class=\"slide__btn--cvn\">\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"/contact/\"><span>お問い合わせ</span></a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/catalog/\"><span>資料請求</span></a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div><!--globalmenu-->\n    <div class=\"min__menu\">\n     <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/news/\"><i class=\"ri-arrow-drop-right-line\"></i> 新着情報</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/flow/\"><i class=\"ri-arrow-drop-right-line\"></i> お問合せから納品まで</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/faq/\"><i class=\"ri-arrow-drop-right-line\"></i> よくある質問</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/policy/\"><i class=\"ri-arrow-drop-right-line\"></i> プライバシーポリシー</a></li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"tel-spmenu\">\n      <div class=\"tel\">\n       <a href=\"tel:0436403201\" class=\"cover\"></a>\n       <dl class=\"din\">\n        <dt>TEL</dt>\n        <dd>0436-40-3201</dd>\n       </dl>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"time\">受付時間／9:00～17:00（※土・日・祝は除く）</div>\n    </div><!--tel-spmenu-->\n  </nav>\n</header>\n\n<article class=\"pdb0\">\n\n<section class=\"mv mv-about mv-about-content\" data-parallax=\"scroll\" data-position=\"center\" data-speed=\"0.2\" data-natural-width=\"2000\" data-natural-height=\"672\" data-image-src=\"../img/mv.jpg\">\n <div class=\"title\">\n  <h2>私たちについて</h2>\n  <span class=\"din\">ABOUT US</span>\n </div><!--title-->\n <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\n</section><!--mv-->\n\n<div class=\"bread\">\n <ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/\">親和パッケージHOME</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/business/\">私たちについて</a></li>\n  <li>会社概要・ネットワーク</li>\n </ul>\n</div><!--bread-->\n\n<section class=\"outline--container\">\n <div class=\"title\">\n  <h2>会社概要・ネットワーク</h2>\n  <span class=\"din\">OUTLINE & NETWORK</span>\n  <hr>\n </div><!--title-->\n \n <div class=\"select-outline\">\n  <div class=\"insert\">\n   <div class=\"btn\"><a href=\"#profile\"><span>会社概要<i class=\"ri-arrow-down-s-fill\"></i></span></a></div>\n   <div class=\"btn\"><a href=\"#network\"><span>ネットワーク<i class=\"ri-arrow-down-s-fill\"></i></span></a></div>\n   <div class=\"btn\"><a href=\"#partner\"><span>主要取引先<i class=\"ri-arrow-down-s-fill\"></i></span></a></div>\n   <div class=\"btn\"><a href=\"#history\"><span>沿革<i class=\"ri-arrow-down-s-fill\"></i></span></a></div>\n  </div><!--insert-->\n </div><!--select-outline-->\n \n <div class=\"outline--insert outline--insert__profile\">\n  \n  <a id=\"profile\" name=\"profile\"></a>\n  <div class=\"profile--insert\">\n   <div class=\"profile-head\">\n    <div class=\"business-title\">\n     <div class=\"din\">COMPANY PROFILE</div>\n     <h2>会社概要</h2>\n    </div><!--business-title-->\n    <div class=\"pic\">\n     <div class=\"inn\"><img src=\"img/profile.jpg\"/></div>\n    </div>\n   </div><!--profile-head-->\n   <div class=\"oversea-table oversea-table-profile\">\n     <table>\n      <tr>\n       <th>社名</th>\n       <td>親和パッケージ株式会社</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n       <th>本社所在地</th>\n       <td>〒658-0033 <br class=\"sp\"/>神戸市東灘区向洋町西6丁目19番地<br class=\"sp\"/><span class=\"din map-head\"><a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/b7jQZw8FuXijjws97\" target=\"_blank\">Map<i class=\"ri-map-pin-line\"></i></a></span><br/>TEL　078-857-3370（代）FAX　078-857-3376</td>\n      </tr>\n       <tr>\n       <th>代表者</th>\n       <td>代表取締役社長　　重実　敬之</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n       <th>設立</th>\n       <td>1950年（昭和25年）2月</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n       <th>資本金</th>\n       <td>3億円</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n       <th>従業員数</th>\n       <td>約800名（シンワグループ全体：約1,300名） ※2023年度</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n       <th>売上高</th>\n       <td>約180億円（シンワグループ全体：約255億円） ※2023年度</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n       <th>役員</th>\n       <td>\n         <dt>取締役社長</dt>